  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Enjoy this extended sneak peek at Disney's Mulan on Blu-ray and digital.",
      "zh": "請欣賞迪士尼《花木蘭》藍光和數位版的延長預告片。",
      "ja": "ディズニーの『ムーラン』ブルーレイ＆デジタル版の拡張プレビューをお楽しみください。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This way, that's the last one.",
      "zh": "這邊，那是最後一個。",
      "ja": "こちらです、それが最後の一つです。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Gently.",
      "zh": "輕輕地。",
      "ja": "優しく。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mulan, forget the chicken.",
      "zh": "木蘭，忘掉那隻雞。",
      "ja": "ムーラン、鶏のことは忘れて。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It will come back.",
      "zh": "牠會回來的。",
      "ja": "戻ってくるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No!",
      "zh": "不！",
      "ja": "いや！",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mulan, take control of yourself!",
      "zh": "木蘭，控制好自己！",
      "ja": "ムーラン、自分をコントロールして！",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm not sure what I can do.",
      "zh": "我不知道我能做什麼。",
      "ja": "何ができるかわからない。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't get it.",
